<?php
$t = array();
$t[1] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! ku cika alkawurra. An halatta muku dabbobin jin d&atilde;ɗi f&atilde;ce abin da ake karant&atilde;wa a kanku, b&atilde; kun&atilde; m&atilde;su halattar da farauta ba alh&atilde;li kuwa kun&atilde; m&atilde;su harama. Lalle ne, Allah Yan&atilde; hukunta abin da yake nufi.';
$t[2] = 'Ya kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! kada ku halattar da ayyukan ib&atilde;dar Allah game da hajji, kuma da wat&atilde; mai alfarma, kuma da hadaya, kuma da r&atilde;tayar raƙuman hadaya, kuma da m&atilde;su nufin &brvbar;&atilde;ki mai alfarma, sun&atilde; neman falala daga Ubangijinsu da yarda. Kuma idan kun kwance harama, to, ku yi farauta. Kuma kada ƙiyayya da wasu mut&atilde;ne ta ɗauke ku, d&otilde;min sun kange ku daga Masall&atilde;ci Mai alfarma, ga ku yi z&atilde;lunci. Kuma ku taimaki jun&atilde; a kan aikin ƙwarai da taƙawa. Kuma kada ku taimaki juna a kan zunubi da z&atilde;lunci, kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa. Lalle ne Allah Mai tsananin uƙũba ne.';
$t[3] = 'An haramta muku mũshe da jini da n&atilde;man alade da abin da aka ambaci sũnan wanin Allah a gare shi, da m&atilde;ƙararriya da jefaffiya da mai gangar&otilde;wa da s&otilde;kakkiya, da abin da m&atilde;su d&atilde;gi suka ci, f&atilde;ce abin da kuka yanka, da abin da aka yanka a kan gunki (shĩ ma an haramta). Kuma kada ku yi rabo da kibiyoyi na c&atilde;ca wannan f&atilde;siƙanci ne, A yau waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta sun yanke ƙauna daga addininku. Sab&otilde;da haka kada ku ji ts&otilde;ronsu kuma ku ji ts&otilde;roNa. A yau N&atilde; kammal&atilde; muku addininku, Kuma N&atilde; cika ni\'imaTa a kanku, Kuma N&atilde; yarda da Musulunci ya zama addini a gare ku. To, wanda aka sanya wa lalũra a cikin yunwa mai tsanani, b&atilde; yana mai karkata zuwa ga wani zunubi ba, to, lalle ne Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[4] = 'Suna tambayar ka cewa mene ne aka halatta musu? Ka ce: &quot;An halatta muku abũbuwa m&atilde;su d&atilde;ɗi da abin da kuka sanar (farauta) daga m&atilde;su yin mĩki, kun&atilde; m&atilde;su sakinsu daga hannuwanku, kun&atilde; sanar da su daga abin da Allah Ya sanar da ku. To, ku ci daga abin da suka kama sab&otilde;da ku, kuma ku ambaci sunan Allah a kansa, kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa. Lalle ne Allah Mai gaugawar sakamako da yaw&atilde; ne.';
$t[5] = 'A yau an halatta muku abũbuwa m&atilde;su d&atilde;ɗi kuma abincin waɗanda aka bai wa Litt&atilde;fi halal ne a gare ku, kuma abincinku halal ne a gare su, da m&atilde;t&atilde; m&atilde;su k&atilde;mun kai daga muminai da m&atilde;t&atilde; \'y&atilde;\'ya daga waɗanda aka bai wa Litt&atilde;fi a gab&atilde;ninku idan kun je musu da sad&atilde;k&otilde;kinsu, kuna m&atilde;su yin aure, ba masu yin zina ba, kuma b&atilde; m&atilde;su riƙon ab&otilde;kai ba. Kuma wanda ya k&atilde;firta da ĩm&atilde;ni to, lalle ne aikinsa y&atilde; ɓ&atilde;ci, kuma shĩ, a cikin L&atilde;hira, yan&atilde; daga m&atilde;su has&atilde;ra.';
$t[6] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! idan kun t&atilde;shi zuwa ga salla, to, ku wanke fusk&otilde;kinku da hannuwanku zuwa ga magincir&otilde;ri, kuma ku yi sh&atilde;fa ga k&atilde;nunku, kuma ku (wanke) ƙaf&atilde;funku zuwa id&atilde;nun s&atilde;wu biyu. Kuma idan kun kasance m&atilde;su janaba, to, ku yi tsarki, kuma idan kun kasance majinyata, k&otilde; kuwa a kan tafiya, k&otilde; kuwa ɗaya daga gare ku ya zo daga k&atilde;shi, k&otilde; kuka yi sh&atilde;fayyar jun&atilde; da m&atilde;t&atilde;, sa\'an nan ba ku s&atilde;mi ruwa ba to ku yi nufin wuri mai kyau, sa\'an nan ku yi sh&atilde;fa ga fusk&otilde;kinku da hannuwanku daga gare shi. Allah b&atilde; Ya nufi d&otilde;min Ya sanya wani ƙunci a kanku, kuma amma Yan&atilde; nufi d&otilde;min Ya cika ni\'imarSa a kanku, tsamm&atilde;ninku kun&atilde; g&otilde;dewa.';
$t[7] = 'Kuma ku tuna ni\'imar Allah akanku da alkawarinku wanda Ya ɗaure ku da shi, a l&otilde;kacin da kuka ce: &quot;Mun ji kuma mun yi ɗ&atilde;\'a Kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa. Lalle ne Allah Masani ne ga abin da ke a cikin zukata.&quot;';
$t[8] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku kasance m&atilde;su tsayin daka d&otilde;min Allah m&atilde;su shaida da &atilde;dalci. Kuma kada ƙiyayya da wasu mutane ta ɗauke ku a kan b&atilde; z&atilde; ku yi &atilde;dalci ba. Ku yi &atilde;dalci Shĩ ne mafi kusa ga taƙawa. Kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa. Lalle Allah Masani ne ga abin da kuke aikat&atilde;wa.';
$t[9] = 'Allah Y&atilde; yi wa\'adi ga waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai. Sun&atilde; da wata g&atilde;fara da l&atilde;da mai girma.';
$t[10] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta, kuma suka ƙaryat&atilde;, game da &atilde;y&otilde;yinMu, waɗannan su ne ab&otilde;kan wuta.';
$t[11] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku tuna ni\'imar Allah a kanku a l&otilde;kacin da wasu mut&atilde;ne suka yi niyyar su shimfiɗa hannuwansu zuwa gare ku sai Ya kange hannuwansu daga gare ku, kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa. Kuma sai muminai su dogara ga Allah kawai.';
$t[12] = 'Kuma lalle Allah Y&atilde; riƙi alkawarin Banĩ lsr&atilde;\' ĩla kuma Muka ayyana wakilai g&otilde;ma sh&atilde; biyu daga gare su kuma Allah Ya ce: &quot;Lalle ne Nĩ, In&atilde; t&atilde;re da ku, haƙĩƙa, idan kun tsayar da salla, kuma kun b&atilde;yar da zakka, kuma kun yi ĩmani da manzannĩNa, kuma kuka taimake su, kuma kuka bai wa Allah rance mai kyau, haƙĩƙa, In&atilde; kankare laifukanku daga gare ku, kuma haƙĩƙa, In&atilde; shigar da ku gid&atilde;jen Aljanna (waɗanda) ƙ&otilde;ramu san&atilde; gud&atilde;na a ƙarƙashinsu, sa\'an nan wanda ya k&atilde;firta a b&atilde;yan wannan daga gare ku, to, lalle ne, y&atilde; ɓace daga tsakar hanya.&quot;';
$t[13] = 'To, sab&otilde;da warwarewarsu ga alkawarinsu Muka la\'ane su, kuma Muka sanya zuk&atilde;tansu ƙeƙasassu, sun&atilde; karkatar da magana daga wur&atilde;renta, kuma suka manta da wani yanki daga abin da aka tun&atilde;tar da su da shi, kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; ka gushe ba kana tsink&atilde;yar yaudara daga gare su f&atilde;ce kaɗan daga gare su. To, ka y&atilde;fe laifi daga gare su, kuma ka kau da kai. Lalle ne, Allah Yan&atilde; son m&atilde;su kyautat&atilde;wa.';
$t[14] = 'Kuma daga waɗanda suka ce: &quot;Lalle ne mu Nas&atilde;ra ne&quot; Mun riƙi alkawarinsu, sai suka manta da wani yanki daga abin da aka tun&atilde;tar da su da shi, sai Muka shushuta ad&atilde;wa da ƙeta a tsak&atilde;ninsu har ya zuwa ga R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma. Kuma Allah zai b&atilde; su l&atilde;bari da abin da suka kasance sun&atilde; san&atilde;\'antawa.';
$t[15] = 'Y&atilde; Mut&atilde;nen litt&atilde;fi! Lalle ne, ManzonMu y&atilde; je muku, yan&atilde; bayyana muku abu mai yawa daga abin da kuka kasance kun&atilde; ɓ&otilde;yewa daga Litt&atilde;fi, kuma yan&atilde; rangwame daga abu mai yawa. Haƙĩƙa, wani haske da wani Littafi mai bayyan&atilde;wa y&atilde; je muku daga Allah.';
$t[16] = 'Dashĩ, Allah Yan&atilde; shiryar da wanda ya bi yardarsa zuwa ga hany&otilde;yin aminci, kuma Yan&atilde; fitar da su daga duffai zuwa ga haske da izninsa, kuma Yan&atilde; shiryar da su zuwa ga hanya madaidaiciya.';
$t[17] = 'Lalle haƙĩƙa waɗanda suka ce: &quot;Lalle Allah Shĩ ne Masĩhu ɗan Maryama,&quot; sun k&atilde;firta. Ka ce: &quot;To, wane ne ke iya mallakar wani abu daga Allah, idan Y&atilde; nufi Ya halakar da Masĩhu ɗanMaryama da uwarsa da wanda yake a cikin ƙasa gab&atilde; ɗaya?&quot; Kuma Allah ne da mallakar sammai da ƙasa da abin da ke a tsak&atilde;ninsu, Yan&atilde; halitta abin da Yake so. Kuma Allah a kan dukkan k&otilde;me, Mai ĩkon yi ne.';
$t[18] = 'Kuma Yahudu da Nas&atilde;ra sun ce: &quot;Mu ne ɗiyan Allah, kuma mas&otilde;yansa.&quot; Ka ce: &quot;To, don me Yake yi muku az&atilde;ba da zunubanku? &Atilde;\'a ku mut&atilde;ne ne daga waɗanda Ya halitta, Yan&atilde; g&atilde;fart&atilde;wa ga wanda Yake so, kuma Yan&atilde; azabta wanda Yake so. Kuma Allah ne da mulkin sammai da ƙasa da abin da ke tsak&atilde;ninsu kuma zuwa gare shi makom&atilde; take.&quot;';
$t[19] = 'Y&atilde; Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi! Lalle ManzonMu y&atilde; je muku yan&atilde; bayyana muku, a kan l&otilde;kacin fatara daga manzanni, d&otilde;min kada ku ce: &quot;wani mai bayar da bush&atilde;ra bai zo mana ba, kuma haka wani mai gargaɗi bai zo ba.&quot; To, haƙĩƙa, mai b&atilde;yar da bush&atilde;ra da mai gargaɗi sunje muku. Kuma Allah ne, a kan dukkan k&otilde;me, Mai ĩkon yi.';
$t[20] = 'Kuma a l&otilde;kacin da Musa ya ce wa mut&atilde;nensa: &quot;Y&atilde; ku mut&atilde;nena! Ku tuna ni\'imar Allah a kanku; d&otilde;min Y&atilde; sanya annab&atilde;wa a cikinku, kuma Y&atilde; sanya ku sar&atilde;kuna, kuma Y&atilde; b&atilde; ku abin da bai bai wa k&otilde;wa ba daga t&atilde;likai.&quot;';
$t[21] = '&quot;Y&atilde; mut&atilde;nena! Ku shiga ƙasar nan, abar tsarkakewa, wadda Allah Ya rubuta sab&otilde;da ku, kuma kada ku k&otilde;ma da b&atilde;ya, har ku juya kun&atilde; m&atilde;su hasara.&quot;';
$t[22] = 'Suka ce: &quot;Ya Mus&atilde;! Lalle ne, a cikinta akwai wasu mut&atilde;ne m&atilde;su ƙarfi kuma lalle ne b&atilde; z&atilde; mu shige ta ba sai sun fice daga gare ta, to, idan sun fice daga gare ta, to, lalle ne mu, masu shiga ne.&quot;';
$t[23] = 'Wasu maza biyu daga waɗanda suke ts&otilde;ron Allah, Allah Y&atilde; yi ni\'ima a kansu, suka ce: &quot;Ku shiga gare su, daga ƙ&otilde;far, d&otilde;min idan kuka shige shi, to, lalle ne ku, m&atilde;su rinj&atilde;ya ne, kuma ga Allah sai ku dogara idan kun kasance muminai.&quot;';
$t[24] = 'Suka ce: &quot;Ya Musa! Lalle ne mu, b&atilde; za mu shige ta ba har abada matuƙar sun dawwama a cikinta sai ka tafi kai da Ubangijinka d&otilde;min ku yi y&atilde;ƙi. Lalle ne mu, mun&atilde; a nan zaune.&quot;';
$t[25] = 'Ya ce: &quot;Y&atilde; Ubangijina! Lalle ne nĩ, b&atilde; ni mallakar k&otilde;wa f&atilde;ce kaina da ɗan\'uw&atilde;na, sai Ka rarrabe a tsak&atilde;ninmu da tsak&atilde;nin mut&atilde;ne f&atilde;siƙai.&quot;';
$t[26] = '(Allah) Ya ce: &quot;To, lalle ne ita abar haramt&atilde;wa ce a gare su, shekara arba\'in, sun&atilde; yin ɗimuwa a cikin ƙasa. Sab&otilde;da haka kada ka yi baƙin ciki a kan mut&atilde;ne f&atilde;siƙai.&quot;';
$t[27] = 'Kuma karant&atilde; musu l&atilde;b&atilde;rin ɗiya biyu na &Atilde;damu, da gaskiya, a l&otilde;kacin da suka b&atilde;yar da baiko, sai aka karɓa daga ɗayansu kuma ba a karɓa daga ɗayan ba, ya ce: &quot;Lalle ne zan kashe ka.&quot; (&brvbar;ayan kuma) ya ce: &quot;Abin sani dai, Allah Yana karɓ&atilde; daga m&atilde;su taƙawa ne.&quot;';
$t[28] = '&quot;Lalle ne idan ka shimfiɗa hannunka zuwa gare ni d&otilde;min ka kashe ni, ban zama mai shimfiɗa hannuna zuwa gare ka ba d&otilde;min in kashe ka. Lalle ne nĩ in&atilde; ts&otilde;ron Allah Ubangijin t&atilde;likai.';
$t[29] = '&quot;Lalle ne nĩ in&atilde; nufin ka k&otilde;ma da zunubina game da zunubinka, har ka kasance daga ab&otilde;kan wuta. Kuma wannan shĩ ne sakamakon azz&atilde;lumai.&quot;';
$t[30] = 'Sai ransa ya ƙaw&atilde;tar masa kashewar ɗan\'uwansa, sai kuwa ya kashe shi, sa\'an nan ya wayi gari daga m&atilde;su has&atilde;ra.';
$t[31] = 'Sai Allah Ya aiki wani hank&atilde;ka, yan&atilde; t&otilde;no a cikin ƙasa d&otilde;min ya nuna masa yadda zai turbuɗe g&atilde;war ɗan\'uwansa. Ya ce: &quot;Kait&otilde;na! N&atilde; k&atilde;sa in kasance kamar wannan hank&atilde;ka d&otilde;min in turbuɗe g&atilde;war ɗan\'uwana?&quot; Sai ya w&atilde;yi gari daga m&atilde;su nad&atilde;m&atilde;.';
$t[32] = 'Daga sababin wannan, Muka rubuta a kan Banĩ lsr&atilde;\'ĩla cewa, lalle ne wanda ya kashe rai b&atilde; da wani rai ba, ko ɓarna a cikin ƙasa, to kamar y&atilde; kashe mut&atilde;ne duka ne, kuma wanda ya r&atilde;ya rai, to, kamar y&atilde; r&atilde;yar da mut&atilde;ne ne gab&atilde; ɗaya. Kuma lalle ne, haƙĩƙa, ManzanninMu sun je musu da hujj&otilde;ji bayyanannu, sa\'an nan kuma lalle ne, m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, a b&atilde;yan wannan, haƙĩƙa, m&atilde;suɓarna ne a cikin ƙasa.';
$t[33] = 'Abin sani kawai sakamakon waɗanda suke Y&atilde;ƙin Allah da Manzonsa, kuma sun&atilde; aiki a cikin ƙasa d&otilde;min ɓarna a kashe su ko kuwa a ƙere su, k&otilde; kuwa a kakk&atilde;tse hannuwansu da ƙaf&atilde;funsu daga s&atilde;ɓ&atilde;ni, ko kuwa a k&otilde;re su daga ƙasa. Sannan gare su wulakanci ne a cikin r&atilde;yuwar duniya, kuma a L&atilde;hira sun&atilde; da wata az&atilde;ba mai girma.';
$t[34] = 'F&atilde;ce fa waɗanda suka tuba tun a gab&atilde;nin ku s&atilde;mi ĩko akansu, to, ku sani cewa lalle ne, Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[35] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma ku nemi tsari zuwa gare shi, kuma ku yi jih&atilde;di a cikin hanyarsa, tsamm&atilde;ninku, za ku ci nasara.';
$t[36] = 'Lalle ne waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta, lalle d&atilde; sun&atilde; da abin da ke a cikin ƙasa gab&atilde; ɗaya da mis&atilde;linsa t&atilde;re da shi, d&otilde;min su yi fansa da shi daga az&atilde;bar R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma, b&atilde; a karɓarsa daga gare su, kuma sun&atilde; da az&atilde;ba mai raɗadi.';
$t[37] = 'Sun&atilde; nufin su fita ne daga wuta, kuma ba su zama m&atilde;su fita daga gare ta ba, kuma sun&atilde; da az&atilde;ba zaunanniya.';
$t[38] = 'Kuma ɓar&atilde;wo da ɓarauniya sai ku yanke hannuwansu, bisa sakamako ga abin da suka tsirfanta, a kan az&atilde;ba daga Allah. Kuma Allah Mabuw&atilde;yi ne, Mai hikima.';
$t[39] = 'To, wanda ya tuba a b&atilde;yan z&atilde;luncinsa, kuma ya gy&atilde;ra (halinsa), to, lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; karɓar tubarsa. Lalle Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[40] = 'Shin, ba ka sani ba cewa lalle ne, Allah Shi ne da mulkin sammai da ƙasa, Yan&atilde; az&atilde;btar da wanda Yake so, kuma Yan&atilde; yin g&atilde;fara ga wanda yake so, kuma Allah a dukkan k&otilde;me, Mai ĩkon yi ne?';
$t[41] = 'Y&atilde; kai Manzo! Kada waɗanda suke tseren gaugawa a cikin k&atilde;firci su ɓ&atilde;ta maka rai, daga waɗanda suka ce: &quot;Mun yi ĩm&atilde;ni&quot; da b&atilde;kunansu, alh&atilde;li zukatansu ba su yi ĩm&atilde;nin ba, kuma daga waɗanda suka tuba (watau Yahudu) m&atilde;su yawan saurare ga wasu mutane na dabam waɗanda ba su je maka ba, sun&atilde; karkatar da zance daga b&atilde;yan wurarensa, sun&atilde; cewa: &quot;Idan an b&atilde; ku wannan, to, ku karɓa, kuma idan ba a b&atilde; ku shĩ ba, to, ku yi sauna.&quot;Kuma wanda Allah Ya yi nufin fitinarsa, to b&atilde; z&atilde; ka mallaka masa k&otilde;me ba, daga Allah. Waɗannan ne waɗanda Allah bai yi nufin Ya tsarkake zuk&atilde;tansu ba. Sun&atilde; da kunya a cikin duniya, kuma sun&atilde; da wata az&atilde;ba mai girma a cikin 1&atilde;hira.';
$t[42] = 'M&atilde;su yawan saur&atilde;re ga ƙarya ne, m&atilde;su yawan ci ga haram, to, idan sun zo maka, sai ka yi hukunci a tsak&atilde;ninsu k&otilde; ka bijira daga gare su. Kuma idan ka bijira daga gare su, to, b&atilde; z&atilde; su cuce ka da k&otilde;me ba, kuma idan ka yi hukunci, to, sai ka hukunta a tsak&atilde;ninsu da &atilde;dalci. Lalle ne, Allah Yan&atilde; son m&atilde;su &atilde;dalci.';
$t[43] = 'Kuma y&atilde;ya suke gab&atilde;tar da kai ga hukunci, alh&atilde;li a wurinsu akwai Attaura, a cikinta akwai hukuncin Allah, sa\'an nan kuma sun&atilde; karkacewa a b&atilde;yan wannan? waɗannan b&atilde; muminai ba ne!';
$t[44] = 'Lalle ne Mu, Mun saukar da Attaura, a cikinta akwai shiriya da haske Annab&atilde;wa waɗanda suke sun sallam&atilde;, sun&atilde; yin hukunci da ita ga waɗanda suka tuba (Yahudu), da m&atilde;laman tarbiyya, da manyan malamai ga abin da aka neme su da su tsare daga Litt&atilde;fin Allah, kuma sun kasance, a kansa, m&atilde;su b&atilde; da shaida. To, kada ku ji ts&otilde;ron mut&atilde;ne kuma ku ji ts&otilde;roNa kuma kada ku sayi \'yan kuɗi kaɗan da &atilde;yoyiNa. wanda bai yi hukunci ba da abin da Allah Ya saukar, to, waɗannan su ne kafirai.';
$t[45] = 'Kuma Mun rubuta a kansu, a cikinta cewa, lalle (an&atilde; kashe) rai sab&otilde;da rai, kuma (an&atilde; ɗebe) id&otilde; sab&otilde;da id&otilde;, kuma (ana katse) hanci sab&otilde;da hanci, kuma kunne sab&otilde;da kunne kuma haƙori sab&otilde;da haƙ&otilde;ri kuma a raunuka a yi sakayya. To, wanda ya yi sadaka da shi, to, shi kaff&atilde;ra ce a gare shi. Kuma wanda bai yi hukunci ba da abin da Allah Ya saukar, to, waɗannan su ne azz&atilde;lumai.';
$t[46] = 'Kuma Muka biyar a kan gur&atilde;bansu da Ĩsa ɗan Maryama, y&atilde;n&atilde; mai gaskat&atilde;wa ga abin da yake a gaba gare shi daga Attaura, kuma Muka b&atilde; shi Injĩla a cikinsa akwai shiriya da haske, yan&atilde; mai gaskat&atilde;wa ga abin da yake a gaba gare shi daga Attaura, kuma shi shiriya ne da wa\'azi ga m&atilde;su taƙawa.';
$t[47] = 'Kuma sai mut&atilde;nen injĩla su yi hukunci da abin da Allah ya saukar a cikinta. Kuma wanda bai yi hukunci ba da abin da Allah ya saukar, to, waɗannan su ne f&atilde;siƙai.';
$t[48] = 'Kuma Mun saukar da Litt&atilde;fi zuwa gare ka da gaskiya, yan&atilde; mai gaskat&atilde;wa ga abin da yake a gaba gare shi daga Litt&atilde;fi (Attaura da Injĩla), kuma mai halart&atilde;wa a kansa. sai ka yi hukunci a tsak&atilde;ninsu da abin da Allah Ya saukar kuma kada ka bĩbiyi son zũciy&otilde;yiniu daga abin da ya zo maka daga gaskiya. Ga k&otilde;wanne daga gare ku Mun sanya sharĩa da hanya (ta bin ta). Kuma d&atilde; Allah Y&atilde; so, d&atilde; Y&atilde; sanya ku al\'umma guda, kuma amma d&otilde;min Ya jarraba ku a cikin abin da Ya b&atilde; ku. Sai ku yi tsere ga ayyukan alheri. Zuwa ga Allah mak&otilde;marku take gab&atilde; ɗaya. Sa\'an nan Ya b&atilde; ku l&atilde;b&atilde;ri ga abin da kuka kasance kun&atilde; s&atilde;ɓ&atilde;wa a cikinsa.';
$t[49] = 'Kuma ka yi hukunci a tsak&atilde;ninsu da abin da Allah Ya saukar kuma kada ka bĩbiyi son zũciy&otilde;yinsu, kuma ka yi saunar su fitine ka daga s&atilde;shen abin da Allah Ya saukar zuwa gare ka. To, idan sun juya b&atilde;ya, to, ka sani cewa, kawai Allah yana nufin Ya s&atilde;me su da masĩfa ne sab&otilde;da s&atilde;shen zunubansu. Kuma lalle ne, m&atilde;su yawa daga mut&atilde;ne, haƙĩƙa, f&atilde;siƙai ne.';
$t[50] = 'Shin, hukuncin J&atilde;hiliyya suke nema? Kuma wane ne mafi kyau ga hukunci daga Allah sab&otilde;da mut&atilde;ne waɗanda suke yin yaƙĩni (tabbataccen ĩm&atilde;ni)?';
$t[51] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku riƙi Yahudu da Nas&atilde;ra majiɓinta. S&atilde;shensu majiɓinci ne ga s&atilde;she. Kuma wanda ya jiɓince su daga gare ku, to, lalle ne shĩ, yan&atilde; daga gare su. Lalle Allah b&atilde; Ya shiryar da mut&atilde;ne azz&atilde;lumai.';
$t[52] = 'Sai ka ga waɗanda a cikin zukatansu akwai cuta, sun&atilde; tseren gaugawa a cikinsu, sun&atilde; cewa: &quot;Mun&atilde; ts&otilde;ron kada wata masĩfa ta s&atilde;me mu.&quot; To, akwai tsamm&atilde;nin Allah Ya zo da buɗi, k&otilde; kuwa wani umurni daga wurinSa, har su w&atilde;yi gari a kan abin da suka ɓ&otilde;ye a cikin zukatansu, sun&atilde; m&atilde;su nad&atilde;m&atilde;.';
$t[53] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni sun&atilde; cewa: &quot;Shin, waɗannan ne waɗanda suka yi rantsuwa da Allah iy&atilde;kar rantsuw&otilde;yinsu, cewa su, lalle sun&atilde; t&atilde;re da ku?&quot; Ayyukansu sun ɓ&atilde;ci, sab&otilde;da haka suka w&atilde;yi gari sun&atilde; m&atilde;su has&atilde;ra.';
$t[54] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! wanda ya yi ridda daga gare ku daga addininSa, to, Allah zai zo da wasu mut&atilde;ne, Yan&atilde; son su kuma sun&atilde; son Sa, m&atilde;su taw&atilde;lu\'i a kan muminai m&atilde;su izza a kan k&atilde;furai. Sun&atilde; yin, jih&atilde;di a cikin hanyar Allah, kuma b&atilde; su ts&otilde;ron zargin wani mai zargi. Waccan falalar Allah ce, Yan&atilde; b&atilde;yar da ita ga wanda Yake so. Kuma Allah Mayalwaci ne, Mai ilmi.';
$t[55] = 'Abin sani kawai, majiɓincinku Allah ne da ManzonSa da waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, waɗanda suke sun&atilde; tsayar da salla kuma sun&atilde; b&atilde;yar da zakka kuma sun&atilde; ruku\'i,';
$t[56] = 'Kuma wanda ya jiɓinci Allah da ManzonSa da waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, to, ƙungiyar Allah sune m&atilde;su rinj&atilde;ya.';
$t[57] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku riƙi waɗanda suka riƙi addininku bisa izgili da w&atilde;sa, daga waɗanda aka bai wa Litt&atilde;fi daga gab&atilde;ninku da k&atilde;firai, mas&otilde;ya, Kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa idan kun kasance muminai.';
$t[58] = 'Kuma idan kuka yi kira zuwa ga salla, sai su riƙe ta bisa izgili da w&atilde;sa. Wannan d&otilde;min lalle ne su, mut&atilde;ne ne (waɗanda) b&atilde; su hankalta.';
$t[59] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Ya Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi! Shin, kun&atilde; ganin wani laifi daga gare mu? F&atilde;ce dai d&otilde;min mun yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah da abin da aka Saukar zuwa gare mu da abin da aka saukar daga gab&atilde;ni, kuma d&otilde;min mafi yawanku f&atilde;siƙai ne.&quot;';
$t[60] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Shin, in gaya muku mafi sharri daga wannan, d&otilde;min sakamako daga wurin Allah? wanda Allah Ya la\'ane shi kuma Ya yi fushi da shi, kuma Ya sanya daga gare su birai da aladai, kuma ya bauta wa &brvbar;&atilde;guta. Waɗannan ne mafiya sharrin wuri, kuma mafiya ɓata daga tsakar hanya.&quot;';
$t[61] = 'Kuma idan sun zo muku sai su ce: &quot;Mun yi ĩm&atilde;ni.&quot; Alh&atilde;li kuwa haƙĩƙa, sun shigo da k&atilde;firci, kuma su lalle ne, sun fita da shi, kuma Allah ne Mafi sani ga abin da suka kasance sun&atilde; ɓ&otilde;yewa.';
$t[62] = 'Kuma kana ganin m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, sun&atilde; tseren gaugawa a cikin zunubi da z&atilde;lunci da cinsu ga haram. Haƙĩƙa, tir da abin da suka kasance suna aikat&atilde;wa.';
$t[63] = 'Don me Malaman Tarbiyya da manyan malamai (na Yahudu) ba su han&atilde; su daga faɗarsu ga zunubi da cinsu ga haram ba? Haƙiƙa, tir daga abin da suka kasance sun&atilde; san&atilde;\'ant&atilde;wa.';
$t[64] = 'Kuma Yahudu suka ce: &quot;Hannun Allah abin yi wa ƙuƙumi ne. &quot; An sanya hannuwansu a cikin ƙuƙumi! Kuma an la\'ane su sab&otilde;da abin da suka faɗa. &Atilde;\'a, hannuwanSa biyu shimfiɗaɗɗu ne, Yan&atilde; ciyarwa yadda Yake so. Kuma lalle ne abin da aka saukar zuwa gare ka yan&atilde; ƙ&atilde;ra wa m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, girman kai da k&atilde;firci. Kuma Mun jefa a tsak&atilde;ninsu, ƙiyayya da ƙeta, zuwa R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma, k&otilde; da yaushe suka hura wata wuta d&otilde;min y&atilde;ƙi, sai Allah Ya bice ta. Sun&atilde; aiki a cikin ƙasa d&otilde;min ɓarna, alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah b&atilde; Ya son m&atilde;su fas&atilde;di.';
$t[65] = 'Kuma d&atilde; dai lalle Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi sun yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma sun yi taƙawa, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; Mun kankare miy&atilde;gun ayyukansu daga gare su, kuma d&atilde; Mun shigar da su gid&atilde;jen Aljannar Ni\'ima.';
$t[66] = 'Kuma d&atilde; dai lalle su, sun tsayar da Attaura da Injĩla da abin da aka saukar zuwa gare su daga Ubangijinsu, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; sun ci daga bisansu da kuma daga ƙarƙashin ƙaf&atilde;funsu. Daga gare su akwai wata al\'umma mai tsakait&atilde;wa kuma m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, abin da suke aikatawa y&atilde; munana.';
$t[67] = 'Y&atilde; kai Manzo! Ka iyar da abin da aka saukar zuwa gare ka daga Ubangijinka. Kuma idan ba ka aikata ba, to, ba ka iyar da manzancinSa ba ke nan. Kuma Allah Yan&atilde; tsare ka daga mut&atilde;ne. Lalle ne, Allah b&atilde; Ya shiryar da mut&atilde;ne k&atilde;firai.';
$t[68] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Y&atilde; ku Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi! Ba ku zama a kan k&otilde;me ba, sai kun tsayar da Attaura da Injĩla da abin da aka saukar zuwa gare ku daga Ubangijinku.&quot;Kuma lalle ne, abin da aka saukar zuwa gare ka daga Ubangijinka, yan&atilde; ƙara wa m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su girman kai da k&atilde;firci. To, kada ka yi baƙin ciki a kan mut&atilde;ne k&atilde;firai.';
$t[69] = 'Lalle ne, waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni da waɗanda sukatuba (Yahũdu) da Karkatattu da Nas&atilde;ra, wanda ya yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allahda R&atilde;nar L&atilde;hira, kuma ya aikata aiki na ƙwarai, to, b&atilde;bu ts&otilde;ro a kansu, kuma b&atilde; su zamo sun&atilde; baƙin ciki ba.';
$t[70] = 'Lalle ne haƙĩƙa Mun riƙi alkawarin Bani Isr&atilde;\'ĩla, kumaMun aiki manzanni zuwa gare su, ko da yaushe wani manzo ya je musu da abin da r&atilde;yukansu b&atilde; su so, wani ɓangare sun ƙaryata, kuma wani ɓangare sun&atilde; kashewa,';
$t[71] = 'Kuma suka yi zaton cewa wata fitina b&atilde; z&atilde; ta kasance ba sai Suka makanta, kuma suka kurubta, sa\'an nan Allah Ya karɓi tuba a gare su, sa\'an nan suka makanta kuma suka kurunta m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, alh&atilde;li Allah Mai gani ne ga abin da suke aikat&atilde;wa.';
$t[72] = 'Lalle ne haƙĩƙa waɗanda suka ce: &quot;Lalle ne Allah, shĩne Masĩhu, ɗan Maryama,&quot; sun k&atilde;firta. Alh&atilde;li kuwa Masĩhu y&atilde; ce: &quot;Y&atilde; Banĩ Isr&atilde;\'ĩla! Ku bauta wa Allah Ubangijina, kuma Ubangijinku.&quot; Lalle ne shĩ, wanda ya yi shirki da Allah, to, lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; haramta masa Aljanna. Kuma b&atilde;bu wasu mataimaka ga azz&atilde;lumai.';
$t[73] = 'Lalle ne, haƙĩƙa, waɗanda suka ce: &quot;Allah na ukun uku ne,&quot; sun k&atilde;firta, kuma babu wani abin baut&atilde;wa f&atilde;ce Ubangji Guda. Kuma idan ba su hanu daga abin da suke faɗa ba, haƙĩƙa, wata az&atilde;ba mai raɗaɗi t&atilde;n&atilde; sh&atilde;far waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta daga gare su.';
$t[74] = 'shin f&atilde;, b&atilde; su tuba zuwa ga Allah, kuma su neme Shi g&atilde;fara, alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai jin ƙai?';
$t[75] = 'Masĩhu ɗan Maryama bai zama ba f&atilde;ce Manzo ne kawai, haƙĩƙa, manzanni sun shige dage gab&atilde;ninsa, kuma uwarsa siddika ce. Sun kasance sun&atilde; cin abinci. Ka duba yadda Muke bayyana musu &atilde;y&otilde;yi. Sa\'an nan kuma ka duba yadda ake karkatar da su.';
$t[76] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Ashe kun&atilde; bauta wa, baicin Allah, abin da ba ya mallakar wata cuta sab&otilde;da ku kuma haka wani amfani alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah Shi ne Mai ji, Masani?&quot;';
$t[77] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Y&atilde; ku Mutanen Litt&atilde;fi! Kada ku zurfafa a cikin addininku, abin da b&atilde; gaskiya ba, kuma kada ku bĩbiyi son zuciy&otilde;yin waɗansu mut&atilde;ne waɗanda suka riga suka ɓace a gab&atilde;ni, kuma suka ɓatar da wasu m&atilde;su yawa, kuma suka ɓace daga tsakar hanya.&quot;';
$t[78] = 'An la\'ani waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta daga Banĩ Isr&atilde;\'ĩla a kan harshen D&atilde;wuda da Ĩsa ɗan Maryama. wannan kuwa sab&otilde;da s&atilde;ɓ&atilde;war da suka yi ne, kuma sun kasance suna ta\'addi.';
$t[79] = 'Sun kasance b&atilde; su hana juna daga abin ƙi, wanda suka aikata. Haƙĩƙa abin da suka kasancesun&atilde; aikat&atilde;wa y&atilde; munana.';
$t[80] = 'Kana ganin m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, sun&atilde; jiɓintar waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta. Haƙĩƙa tir da abin da r&atilde;yukansu suka gab&atilde;tar sab&otilde;da su, watau Allah Y&atilde; yi fushi da su, kuma a cikin az&atilde;ba su m&atilde;su dawwama ne';
$t[81] = 'Kuma d&atilde; sun kasance sun&atilde; ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah da Annabi da abin da aka saukar zuwa gare shi, d&atilde; ba su riƙe su mas&otilde;ya ba. Kuma amma m&atilde;su yawa daga gare su, f&atilde;siƙai ne.';
$t[82] = 'Lalle ne kana s&atilde;mun mafiya tsananin mut&atilde;ne a ad&atilde;wa ga waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, Yahudu ne da waɗanda suka yi shirki. Kuma lalle ne kan&atilde; s&atilde;mun mafiya kusantarsu a s&otilde;yayya ga waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni su ne waɗanda suka ce: &quot;Lalle mu ne Nas&atilde;ra.&quot; Wancan kuwa sab&otilde;da akwai &iexcl;issawa da ruhub&atilde;n&atilde;wa daga cikinsu. Kuma lalle ne su, b&atilde; su yin girman kai.';
$t[83] = 'Kuma idan suka ji abin da aka saukar zuwa ga Manzo, kan&atilde; ganin idanunsu sun&atilde; zubar da haw&atilde;ye, sab&otilde;da abin da suka sani daga gaskiya, sun&atilde; cewa: &quot;Y&atilde; Ubangijinmu! Mun yi ĩm&atilde;ni, sai ka rubuta mu t&atilde;re da m&atilde;su shaida.';
$t[84] = '&quot;Kuma mene ne yake gare mu, b&atilde; z&atilde; mu yi ĩm&atilde;ni daAllah ba, da kuma abin da ya zo mana daga gaskiya, kuma mun&atilde; gurin Ubangijinmu Ya shigar da mu t&atilde;re da mut&atilde;ne s&atilde;lihai?&quot;';
$t[85] = 'Sab&otilde;da haka, Allah Y&atilde; s&atilde;k&atilde; musu, d&otilde;min abin da suka faɗa da gid&atilde;jen Aljanna (waɗanda) ƙ&otilde;ramu sun&atilde; gud&atilde;na a ƙarƙashinsu, sun&atilde; madawwama a cikinsu, kuma wannan ne sakamakon m&atilde;su kyautat&atilde;wa.';
$t[86] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta kuma suka ƙaryata game da &atilde;y&otilde;yinMu, waɗancan ne ab&otilde;kan Wuta.';
$t[87] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku haramta abubuwa m&atilde;su d&atilde;ɗi da Allah Ya halatta muku, kuma kada ku ƙetare haddi. Lalle ne, Allah b&atilde; Ya son m&atilde;su ƙetare haddi.';
$t[88] = 'Kuma ku ci daga abin da Allah Ya azurta ku, halat mai daɗi, kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa, wanda yake ku, m&atilde;su ĩm&atilde;ni ne da shi.';
$t[89] = 'Allah b&atilde; Ya k&atilde;m&atilde; ku sab&otilde;da y&atilde;sassa a cikin rantsuw&otilde;yinku, kuma amma Yan&atilde; k&atilde;m&atilde; ku da abin da kuka ƙudurta rantsuw&otilde;yi (a kansa). To, kaff&atilde;rarsa ita ce ciyar da miskĩni g&otilde;ma daga matsakaicin abin da kuke ciyar da iy&atilde;lanku, k&otilde; kuwa tuf&atilde;tar da su, k&otilde; kuwa \'yant&atilde;war wuya. Sa\'an nan wanda bai s&atilde;mu ba, sai azumin kw&atilde;na uku. wannan ne kaff&atilde;rar rantsuw&otilde;yinku, idan kun rantse. Kuma ku kiy&atilde;ye rantsuwoyinku. Kamar wannan ne Allah Yake bayyana muku &atilde;yoyinsa, tsamm&atilde;ninku kun&atilde; g&otilde;dewa.';
$t[90] = 'Ya ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Abin sani kawai, giya da c&atilde;ca da refu da kiban ƙuri\'a, ƙazanta ne daga aikin shaiɗan, sai ku nĩsance shi, wa la\'alla ku ci nasara.';
$t[91] = 'Abin sani kawaĩ Shaiɗan yan&atilde; nufin ya aukar da ad&atilde;wa da ƙeta a tsak&atilde;ninku, a cikin giya da c&atilde;ca, kuma ya kange ku daga ambaton Allah, kuma daga sallah. To, shin, ku m&atilde;su hanuwa ne?';
$t[92] = 'Ku yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Allah, kuma ku yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Manzo, kuma ku kiy&atilde;ye. To, idan kun jũya, to, ku sani abin da kawai yake kan ManzonMu, iyarwa bayyananniya.';
$t[93] = 'B&atilde;bu laifi a kan waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai, a cikin abin da suka ci, idan sun yi taƙawa kuma suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai, sa\'an nan suka yi taƙawa kuma suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, sa\'an nan kuma suka yi taƙawa kuma suka kyautata. Kuma Allah Yana son m&atilde;su kyautat&atilde;wa.';
$t[94] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Lalle ne, Allah zai jarraba ku da wani abu, daga farauta, hannuwanku da m&atilde;sunku sun&atilde; s&atilde;mun sa d&otilde;min Allah Ya san wanda yake tsoron Sa a fake. To, wanda ya yi ta\'addi a b&atilde;yan wannan, to, yan&atilde; da az&atilde;ba mai raɗaɗi.';
$t[95] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku kashe farauta alh&atilde;li kun&atilde; m&atilde;su harama. Kuma wanda ya kashe shi daga gare ku, yan&atilde; mai ganganci, sai sakamako mis&atilde;lin abin da ya kashe, daga dabb&otilde;bin ni\'ima, ma\'abuta &atilde;dalci biyu daga cikinku sun&atilde; yin hukunci da shi. Ya zama hadaya mai isa ga Ka\'aba ko kuwa kaff&atilde;ra da abincin miskĩnai ko kuwa a matsayinsa ya yi azumi d&otilde;min ya ɗanɗani masifar al\'amarinsa. Allah Y&atilde; yafe laifi daga abin da ya gab&atilde;ta. Kuma wanda ya k&otilde;ma, to, Allah zai yi az&atilde;bar r&atilde;muwa daga gare shi, kuma Allah Mabuw&atilde;yi ne, ma\'abũcin azab&atilde;r r&atilde;muwa.';
$t[96] = 'An halatta muku farautar ruwa da abincinsa d&otilde;min jin d&atilde;ɗi a gare ku, kuma d&otilde;min matafiya. Kuma an haramta farautar tudu a kanku, matuƙar kun dawwama m&atilde;su harama. Kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa, wanda yake zuwa gare Shi ne ake t&atilde;ra ku.';
$t[97] = 'Allah Ya sanya Ka\'aba &brvbar;aki Tsararre, ma\'aunin addini ga mutane, kuma Y&atilde; sanya wat&atilde; Mai alfarma da hadaya da r&atilde;tay&otilde;yin Allah Y&atilde; san abin da yake a cikin sammai da abin da yake a cikin ƙasa, kuma cewa lalle Allah, ga dukkan, k&otilde;me, Masani ne.';
$t[98] = 'Ku sani cewa lalle Allah Mai tsananin uƙuba ne, kuma lalle Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[99] = 'B&atilde;bu abin da yake a kan Manzo, sai iyarwa, kuma Allah Yan&atilde; sanin abin da kuke bayyan&atilde;wa da abin da kuke ɓ&otilde;yewa.';
$t[100] = 'Ka ce: &quot;Mummuna da mai kyau b&atilde; su daidaita, kuma k&otilde; d&atilde; yawan mummuan y&atilde; b&atilde; ka sha\'awa. Sab&otilde;da haka ku bi Allah da taƙawa, y&atilde; ma\'abuta hankula ko la\'alla z&atilde; ku ci nasara.&quot;';
$t[101] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku yi tambaya ga abubuwa, idan an bayyana muku (hukuncinsu) su ɓ&atilde;ta muku rai. Kuma idan kuka yi tambaya a gare su a l&otilde;kacin da ake saukar da Alƙur\'&atilde;ni, z&atilde; a bayyana maku. Allah Y&atilde; y&atilde;fe laifi daga gare su, Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai haƙuri.';
$t[102] = 'Lalle ne wasu mut&atilde;ne sun tambaye su daga gab&atilde;ninku, sa\'an nan kuma suka w&atilde;yi gari da su san&atilde; k&atilde;firai.';
$t[103] = 'Kuma Allah bai sanya wata bahĩra ba, kuma haka s&atilde;\'iba, kuma haka wasĩla, kuma haka h&atilde;mi, amma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta, su suke ƙirƙira ƙarya ga Allah, kuma mafi yawansu b&atilde; su hankalta.';
$t[104] = 'Kuma idan aka ce musu: &quot;Ku zo zuwa ga abin da Allah Ya saukar, kuma zuwa ga Manzo,&quot; sai su ce: &quot;Mai isarmu shi ne abin da muka iske ubanninmu a kansa.&quot; Shin, kuma k&otilde; d&atilde; ubanninsu sun kasance b&atilde; su sanin k&otilde;me kuma b&atilde; su shiryuwa?';
$t[105] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku lazimci r&atilde;yukanku, wanda ya ɓace b&atilde; zai cuce ku ba idan kun shiryu, zuwa ga Allah mak&otilde;marku take gab&atilde; ɗaya. Sa\'an nan Ya b&atilde; ku l&atilde;bari ga abin da kuka kasance kun&atilde; aikat&atilde;wa.';
$t[106] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Shaidar tsak&atilde;ninku, idan mutuwa ta halarci ɗayanku, a l&otilde;kacin wasiyya, maza biyu ne ma\'abuta &atilde;dalci daga gare ku, k&otilde; kuwa wasu biyu daga wasunku idan kun tafi a cikin ƙasa sa\'an nan masĩfarmutuwa ta s&atilde;me ku. Kun&atilde; tsare su daga b&atilde;yan salla har su yi rantsuwa da Allah; idan kun yi shakka: &quot;B&atilde; mu sayen kuɗi da shi, k&otilde; d&atilde; ya kasance ma\'abucin zumunta kuma b&atilde; mu ɓ&otilde;ye shaidar Allah. Lalle ne mu, a l&otilde;kacin, haƙĩƙa, mun&atilde; daga m&atilde;su zunubi.&quot;';
$t[107] = 'To, idan aka gane cewa lalle sũ, sun cancanci zunubi to sai wasu biyu su tsayu matsayibsu daga waɗanda suka karɓa daga gare su, mut&atilde;ne biyu mafiya cancanta, sa\'an nan su yi rantsuwa da Allah: &quot;Lalle ne shaidarmu ce mafi gaskiya daga shaidarsu, kuma ba mu yi z&atilde;lunci ba. Lalle mu, a l&otilde;kacin haƙĩƙa, mun&atilde; daga azz&atilde;lumai.&quot;';
$t[108] = 'Wannan ne mafi kusantar su zo da shaida a kan fuskarta k&otilde; kuwa su yi ts&otilde;ron a tũre rantsuw&otilde;yi a b&atilde;yan rantsuw&otilde;yinsu. Kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa kuma ku saurara, kuma Allah b&atilde; Ya shiryar da mut&atilde;ne f&atilde;siƙai.';
$t[109] = 'A ranar da Allah Yake t&atilde;ra manzanni sa\'an nan Ya ce: &quot;Mene ne aka karɓa muku?&quot; (z&atilde;) su ce: &quot;B&atilde;bu ilmi a gare mu. Lalle ne Kai, Kai ne Masanin abubuwan fake.&quot;';
$t[110] = 'A l&otilde;kacin da Allah Ya ce: &quot;Y&atilde; Ĩs&atilde; ɗan Maryama! Ka tuna ni\'ima Ta a kanka, kuma a kan mahaifiyarka, a l&otilde;kacin da Na ƙarfafa ka da Rũhul &iexcl;udusi, kan&atilde; yiwa mut&atilde;ne magana a cikin shimfiɗar jariri, da kuma kan&atilde; dattijo. Kuma a l&otilde;kacin da Na sanar da kai rubutu da hikima da Attaura da Injĩla, kuma a l&otilde;kacin da kake yin halitta daga l&atilde;k&atilde; kamar surar tsuntsu da izinĩNa, sa\'an nan ka hura a cikinta sai ta zama tsuntsu da izinĩNa, kuma kan&atilde; warkar da haifaffen makaho da kuturu, da izinĩNa, kuma a l&otilde;kacin da kake fitar da matattu da izinĩNa, kuma a l&otilde;kacin da Na kange Banĩ Isr&atilde;\'ĩla daga gare ka, a l&otilde;kacin da ka je musu da hujj&otilde;ji bayyanannu, sai waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta daga cikinsu suka ce: \'Wannan b&atilde; k&otilde;me ba ne, f&atilde;ce sihiri bayyananne.\'';
$t[111] = '&quot;Kuma a l&otilde;kacin da Na yi wahayi zuwa ga Haw&atilde;riy&atilde;wa cewa ku yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Ni, kuma da ManzoNa. Suka ce: &quot;Mun yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma ka shaida da cewa lalle mu, m&atilde;su sallam&atilde;wa ne.&quot;';
$t[112] = 'A l&otilde;kacin da Hawar&atilde;y&atilde;wa suka ce: &quot;Ya Ĩsa ɗan Maryam! shin, Ubangijinka Yan&atilde; iy&atilde;wa Ya saukar da kaɓaki a kanmu daga sam&atilde;?&quot; (Ĩs&atilde;) Ya ce: &quot;Ku bi Allah da taƙawa idan kun kasance muminai.&quot;';
$t[113] = 'Suka ce: &quot;Mun&atilde; nufin mu ci daga gare shi ne, kuma zuk&atilde;tanmu su natsu kuma mu san cewa lalle ne, k&atilde; yi mana gaskiya, kuma mu kasance daga m&atilde;su shaida a kansa.&quot;';
$t[114] = 'Ĩs&atilde; ɗan Maryam ya ce: &quot;Y&atilde; Allah. Ubangijinmu! Ka saukar da kaɓaki a kanmu daga sama d&otilde;min ya zama ĩdi ga na farkonmu da na ƙarshenmu, kuma ya zama &atilde;y&atilde; daga gare Ka. Ka azurta mu, kuma Kai ne Mafĩfĩcin m&atilde;su azurtawa.&quot;';
$t[115] = 'Allah Ya ce: &quot;Lalle ne Nĩ mai saukar da shi ne a kanku sa\'an nan wanda ya k&atilde;firta daga gare ku, to, lalle ne Nĩ, In&atilde; azabta shi, da wata az&atilde;ba wadda b&atilde; Ni azabta ta ga k&otilde;wa daga t&atilde;likai.&quot;';
$t[116] = 'Kuma a l&otilde;kacin da Allah Ya ce: &quot;Y&atilde; Ĩs&atilde; ɗan Maryama! Shin, kai ne ka ce wa mut&atilde;ne, \'Ku riƙe ni, ni da uwata, abubuwan baut&atilde;wa biyu, baicin Allah?&quot; (Ĩs&atilde;) Ya ce: &quot;Tsarkinka y&atilde; tabbata! B&atilde; ya kasancewa a gare ni, in faɗi abin da b&atilde;bu wani hakki a gare ni. Idan n&atilde; kasance n&atilde; faɗe shi, to lalle Ka san shi, Kan&atilde; sanin abin da ke a cikin raina, kuma b&atilde; ni sanin abin da ke a cikin nufinKa. Lalle ne Kai Masanin abubuwan fake ne.&quot;';
$t[117] = '&quot;Ban faɗa musu ba f&atilde;ce abin da Ka umurce ni da shi; watau: \'Ku bauta wa Allah Ubangijina kuma Ubangijinku;\' kuma n&atilde; kasance mai shaida a kansu matuƙar n&atilde; dawwama a cikinsu, sa\'an nan a l&otilde;kacin da Ka karɓi raina K&atilde; kasance Kai ne mai tsaro a kansu, kuma Kai, a kan dukkan k&otilde;me, Halartacce ne.';
$t[118] = '&quot;Idan Ka azabta su, to lalle ne su, b&atilde;yinKa ne, kuma idan Ka g&atilde;farta musu, to, lalle ne Kai ne Mabuwayi Mai hikima.&quot;';
$t[119] = 'Allah Ya ce: &quot;Wannan ce r&atilde;nar da m&atilde;su gaskiya, gaskiyarsu take amf&atilde;ninsu. Sun&atilde; da gid&atilde;jen Aljanna, ƙ&otilde;ramu sun&atilde; gud&atilde;na daga ƙarƙashinsu, sun&atilde; madawwama a cikinsu har abada. Allah Y&atilde; yarda da su, kuma sun yarda da Shi. wannan ne babban rabo mai girma.&quot;';
$t[120] = 'Allah ne da mallakar sammai da ƙasa da abin da ke a cikinsu kuma shi, a kan dukkan k&otilde;me Mai ĩkon yi ne.';
?>